    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a first car to learn the ropes on? This vehicle is ready for a fresh start with a dedicated new owner! It definitely shows its age and will require some mechanical attention and bodywork to get it back to its best, but it's a fantastic opportunity for someone handy to breathe new life into a classic workhorse. Grab a bargain and make this car your own!",
